  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE THE DEPARTMENT OF FINANCE AND ADMINISTRATION, ACTING ON BEHALF OF THE MISSISSIPPI DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY, TO SELL AND CONVEY THE FACILITY CURRENTLY USED BY THE HIGHWAY SAFETY PATROL AS ITS TROOP H HEADQUARTERS AND DRIVER SERVICE BUREAU FACILITY, AND ANY IMPROVEMENTS THEREON, LOCATED IN LAUDERDALE COUNTY, MISSISSIPPI, TO COMPASS DATACENTERS JAN I LLC; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
